==Pipil==
===Pronunciation===
* {{a|standard}} {{IPA|ppl|/Ëˆjawi/}}
===Verb===
{{head|ppl|verb}}
# {{lb|ppl|intransitive}} to [[go]], to [[move]] through space
#: {{ux|ppl|'''Yajki''' ka itechan pal kita ne imiakwan|She/he '''went''' to his town to see her/his family}}
#: {{ux|ppl|Nemi pal '''niawi''' nikpanultia muchi tey ne timunekit pal ne shupan|I have to go to move everything we will need for the rainy season}}
# {{lb|ppl|auxiliary}} to be going to (''used to indicate the future'')
#: {{ux|ppl|Ashan '''niu'''-ninaka ka nuchan ika nikukuya|Today I'm '''going''' to stay home because I'm sick}}
====Usage notes====
* In informal speech, the auxiliary verb ''yawi'' to indicate periphrastic future often takes the shortened form ''yu-'' conjugated for the corresponding person with no plural markers.
